Package: optCQR
Type: Package
Title: Optimal Conformalized Quantile Regression
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tianying", "Wang", email = "tianying.wang@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Author: Tianying Wang [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Tianying Wang <tianying.wang@example.com>
Description: Implements the Optimal Conformalized Quantile Regression method.
    Unlike standard CQR which uses fixed symmetric quantiles, optCQR optimizes
    the lower quantile level to minimize prediction interval length while
    maintaining valid coverage. The package also includes standard CQR variants
    (CQR, CQR-m, CQR-r) for comparison. Particularly effective for asymmetric
    conditional distributions.
